Title: I'm Not Her
Writer: Peter Nowalk (created by), Maya Goldsmith, Morenike Balogun (executive story editor), Abby Ajayi (story editor), Sarah L. Thompson (story editor)
Actors: Viola Davis, Billy Brown, Jack Falahee, Aja Naomi King
Plot: While Annalise reconnects with an important client, she continues struggling to move forward. Meanwhile, the "Keating 4" try to move past their tarnished reputations; in flash-forward, details to a tragic crime start unfolding.
